                    "type": "text",
                    "angle": 0,
                    "index": 2,
                    "merge_prev": false,
                    "content": "An option is now provided to ignore tropospheric scatter loss in the diffraction and coverage modules. In the diffraction module, select Options - Diffraction Options and set the scatter method to do not calculate."
